T02TD3653E:263a-1: bha ga ba t'i pradzny'a pa r'a mi t'a s'a dha nam /
T02TD3653E:263a-3: bcom ldan 'das yum shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3653E:263a-4: bcom ldan 'das yum shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3653E:263a-5: sngar bshad pa ltar gdong pa bkru ba la sogs pa byas nas /
T02TD3653E:263a-6: de'i rjes la bdag nyid kyi snying gar padma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i dbus su aa las byung ba'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su yi ge dh'i:/
T02TD3653E:263a-7: de las byung ba'i padma shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i glegs bam gyis mtshan pa /
T02TD3653E:263a-8: 'di dag yongs su gyur pa las /
T02TD3653E:263a-9: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma padma dang /
T02TD3653E:263a-10: zla ba'i gdan la rdo rje skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
T02TD3653E:263a-11: sku mdog dkar ba g-yas kyis mchog sbyin pa /
T02TD3653E:263a-12: g-yon pa na padma bsnams pa /
T02TD3653E:263a-13: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3653E:263a-14: bsam gtan la gcig tu gzhol ba /
T02TD3653E:263a-15: me tog dri zhim pos brgyan pa'i ral pa dang cod pan te /
T02TD3653E:263a-16: re zhig de lta bur bsams la /
T02TD3653E:263a-17: mchod pa'i dus kyi tshe dkyil 'khor gyi gnas su lha brgyad po bdag nyid dang 'dra ba dang lhan cig tu sngags 'dis mchod par bya'o //
T02TD3653E:263b-1: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
